    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Contemporary artists who create outdoor paintings, drawings, or three-dimensional works on walls, sidewalks, or street surfaces in public thoroughfares, sometimes intended to draw attention to urban issues. The term may also refer to anyone routinely creating works outdoors, for example painters who are set up on sidewalks to paint canvases or tatoo artists who decorate customers on sidewalks.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000050638/Ganz, Graffiti World: Street Art (2004)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hedendaagse kunstenaars die in de buitenlucht en op de openbare weg schilderijen, tekeningen of driedimensionale werken op muren, trottoirs of de straat maken, soms bedoeld om de aandacht te vestigen op stedelijke problemen. De term kan ook verwijzen naar iedereen die gewoonlijk in de buitenlucht werkt, zoals schilders of tatoeagekunstenaars die hun werk op trottoirs verrichten.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>主要於牆面、人行道或主要幹道的街道上，進行戶外繪畫、素描或3D作品的創作，有時其目的在於喚起大眾對都市議題的關注。該詞條也指任何慣於戶外創作的人，例如在人行道旁架起畫板畫油畫的畫家，或是替客人刺青的刺青師。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
